    "80e7eb22-860b-4969-81b4-1963a9468091": {
      "type": "about-mission",
      "custom_css": [
        "p,h1,h6,twib-text {font-family: \"Ratch\", sans-serif !important;}"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_809_x_1520_px_809_x_1320_px.png",
        "title": "The Mission.",
        "sub_title": "Setting a new standard for health beverages in New Zealand.",
        "text": "<p>Sibling duo Tom and Belle Hartles spotted a golden opportunity in New Zealand's wellness market and set off to revolutionise it with Goju, aiming to craft not just wellness shots but a whole range wellness drinks that would be unmatched in both quality and effectiveness. </p><p>Their mission began with a bold aim: to make Goju's offerings the global gold standard in wellness beverages.</p><p>What sets Goju apart is its uncompromising ingredient list. Each product, from Goju's pioneering wellness shots to their functional juices, contain a concentration of beneficial components unrivalled by competitors. This dedication to superior quality is why Goju stands out in a crowded market of health claims - Goju’s ingredient list doesn't just talk; it sings.</p><p>Underpinning Tom and Belle's vision was an unwavering commitment to sustainability and local sourcing. Every Goju drink is a testament to this ethos, crafted from the finest organic ingredients New Zealand has to offer, ensuring every sip supports not just the wellbeing of the consumer but the health of the planet too.</p><p>Today, Goju is more than just wellness shots; it's a holistic wellness brand that continues to push the boundaries of innovation. Always striving to be the best in what we do, Goju is a beacon of quality, sustainability, and unparalleled taste in the wellness industry. For those wondering about the price point, we invite you to compare our ingredients list with others on the market. At Goju, we believe in investing in your health, and our products proudly reflect that philosophy.</p>",
        "icon_image": "shopify://shop_images/icons_691a9ebb-fb52-4f41-895c-2648688fa7f6.png"
      }
    },
    "about-sec1": {
      "type": "about-sec1",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "sub_heading": "ABOUT  GOJU",
        "heading": "Goju.  Straight up.",
        "body_text": "<p>In life, it pays to be straight up. It brings the best out in people. It’s gets rid of all the bullshit.</p><p><br/>And leaves you with the bits that matter.<br/></p><p>It gets you places. We’re all about getting places.</p><p><br/>We want to become New Zealand’s favourite go-to health drink. We want to help you get to where you’re going. A little healthier, and a little happier.</p><p><br/>We want to produce New Zealand’s best wellness products and be sold all over the world. Straight up.<br/></p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-banner-img.png",
        "bottom_image": "shopify://shop_images/about-banner-icons.png"
      }
    },
