        "title": "Ingredients.",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "sub_title": "Functional, naturally.",
        "text": "<p>We're dedicated to transparency and quality in every drop. Wondering what goes into our products? Let us break it down for you.</p><p>We pride ourselves on sourcing the freshest, highest-quality ingredients, starting with our ginger and turmeric. While these superstars aren't native to New Zealand, we've forged partnerships with organic farms in Fiji to ensure top-notch supplies. Picture lush fields, rich soil, and sustainable farming practices – that's where our ginger and turmeric come from.</p><p>But that's not all. Our commitment to local sourcing means the rest of our ingredients are sourced from New Zealand's finest farms. We prioritise organic options and support farmers who share our values of fairness and eco-friendliness. Think crisp apples, zesty lemons, and juicy blackcurrants – all carefully selected to bring you the best nature has to offer.</p><p>At Goju, we believe that what you put into your body matters. That's why our products contain no additives, preservatives, or artificial flavourings – just pure, natural goodness. Whether you're looking to boost your immune system, detoxify, or simply fuel your day, you can trust Goju to deliver products that are as good for you as they are delicious.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/GOJU_GINGER500ml_SHOT9_1.png",
        "video": "",
        "link_text": "",
        "url": ""
      }
    },
